instruction.summary: Circle line or District line to Monument
instruction.detailed: Circle line towards Embankment and Tower Hill or District line towards Upminster, or Barking

disruptions.description: Circle Line: Severe delays due to an earlier signal failure at Kings Cross. Tickets will be accepted on London Buses within zone 1.

WIMBLEDON AND WESTMINSTER STATIONS: A ramp is provided at these stations providing step-free access onto District line trains (as well as Circle line trains at Westminster). Please ask staff in the ticket hall at the start of your journey to ensure the ramp will be available when you arrive at your destination.
